<name>Global Intelligence Platform v15 — Week 12 (2 Jul 2026)</name>
<description><![CDATA[Latin America expansion + Economic-Leverage module. 26 theaters in subregion folders + a Venezuela/Caribbean OSINT wargame layer (44 assets, user-provided). New theaters: Venezuela, Colombia, Mexico, Cuba. Sudan RSF Peace-Govt march on El Obeid; Iran-US Doha 1-week truce; Mali Kayes strike; Houthis resume Red Sea. Sources: ISW, ACLED, Crisis Group, Axios, UN OHCHR, US DOJ/Treasury TIC, CRS, Brookings, Registraduria, user OSINT.]]></description>
