<Placemark><name>🇨🇺 Cuba — Post-Intervention Shock + Strangulation</name>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Cuba — Post-Intervention Shock + Strangulation</b><br/><b>Subregion:</b> Caribbean<br/><b>Category:</b> POLITICAL | <b>Domain:</b> Economic Strangulation / Regime Pressure<br/><b>Severity:</b> MEDIUM | <b>Status:</b> STALEMATE<br/><b>Index:</b> 63/100 (Δ ±0)<br/><b>Human cost:</b> 32 Cuban soldiers killed in the Jan 3 Caracas operation (Havana confirmed)<br/><b>Note:</b> NEW THEATER (backfilled) · Havana confirmed 32 Cuban soldiers 'lost their lives in combat' in the Maduro capture; Díaz-Canel: 'state terrorism'; Raúl Castro (94) at the tribute · US strategy explicit: cut Venezuelan oil to Cuba hoping immiseration triggers uprising · Trump: Cuba 'could be next' (Donroe list) · utility crisis: blackouts, fuel shortage, tourism hit; Matanzas relief short-lived (user 52D layer corroborates) · Bejucal SIGINT (China) cross-link retained from Geopolitical theater<br/><b>Gov sources:</b> Cuban Government (official): Confirmed 32 soldiers killed 'carrying out missions' at Venezuela's request; Díaz-Canel condemned 'state terrorism' | US policy (Brookings/CRS synthesis): Oil-to-Cuba interdiction intended to immiserate and spur uprising against the 'Castroite regime'<br/><b>Mil leverage:</b> United States: Venezuela-oil cutoff + embargo + 'next' threat — strangulation without strikes [HIGH] | Cuban state: Security apparatus intact; emigration as pressure valve; martyrdom narrative from the 32 [MED] | China: Bejucal SIGINT + economic lifeline potential — hemispheric counter-presence [MED] | Russia: Symbolic solidarity; limited material capacity while consumed by Ukraine [LOW]<br/><b>Econ leverage:</b> United States (Energy interdiction) [HIGH]: Venezuelan oil lifeline cut deliberately; grid collapse as coercion instrument<br/><b>Assessment:</b> Cuba enters at 63, drifting slightly down as the post-January shock settles into chronic siege. It is the quietest of the four new theaters but structurally coupled to all of them: its oil comes through Venezuela, its threat listing comes from the Donroe Doctrine, and its China link (Bejucal) makes it the one place where hemisphere pressure touches great-power infrastructure. Watch the grid — sustained total blackout is the scenario that historically precedes unrest.<br/><i>v15.0 · Week 12</i>]]></description><styleUrl>#s-political</styleUrl>
